description:
What does the book of Daniel tell us about the #Sabbath? What can we learn from these #prophecies? 

#Daniel reminds us that Jesus is coming soon. #Prophecy tells us exactly that. In this video, we will look through Daniel chapter 2 and chapter 7. In Daniel chapter 7, we find some amazing aspects that are very similar to Daniel chapter 2.

There is a very great attempt to change God's law. The Sabbath is God's seal, His special connection, His understanding for us that he is the Creator that He has authority. The little horn in Daniel will not succeed because God is in control.
